# 二十四、E6 技术设计草图要求

请用 ASCII 图画出 E6 的测试台架构。

必须包含：

```text
Host PC
├── e6_powercut_runner.py
├── e6_serial_logger.py
├── e6_power_control.py
├── e6_target_probe.py
├── e6_result_judge.py
└── e6_report_generator.py

Connections
├── USB serial → i.MX6ULL UART
├── Power control → target low-voltage DC input
└── optional network / SSH, disabled by default

Target
├── U-Boot BOOT_ORDER / BOOT_A_LEFT / BOOT_B_LEFT
├── rootfs_A: /dev/mmcblk0p2
├── rootfs_B: /dev/mmcblk0p3
├── /data: /dev/mmcblk0p4
├── RAUC
├── edgeguard-current-slot
├── S99edgeguard-health
├── watchdog keeper
└── trimmed kernel
```

还要画出单轮测试流程：

```text
baseline probe
→ ensure bundle staged on /data
→ trigger OTA
→ random delay
→ power off
→ power on
→ collect boot log
→ probe state
→ judge result
→ save report
```

